le Glass be cool?  Of course it would be cool.  But I want to be part of an initiative to help low-vision individuals like myself.  I want to help Google develop really adaptive solutions for the small segment of the population that really need adaptive services.  I want Google to help provide vision-related technologies to the visually impaired.<br /><br />Google, are you interested in a real experiment or just a product test drive?  If so, I&#39;m ready to talk.","url":"https://plus.google.com/112039022986516057445/posts/jTNBgfoqchF","replies":{"totalItems":0,"selfLink":"https://www.googleapis.com/plus/v1/activities/z13pd3ozpuf3yzubx04cdvw4hknmu50aagg/comments"},"plusoners":{"totalItems":4,"selfLink":"https://www.googleapis.com/plus/v1/activities/z13pd3ozpuf3yzubx04cdvw4hknmu50aagg/people/plusoners"},"resharers":{"totalItems":0,"selfLink":"https://www.googleapis.com/plus/v1/activities/z13pd3ozpuf3yzubx04cdvw4hknmu50aagg/people/resharers"},"attachments":[{"objectType":"photo","id":"112039022986516057445.5849752824710553362","content":"retina.jpg","url":"https://plus.google.com/photos/112039022986516057445/albums/5849752825405099761/5849752824710553362?authkey=CLTqmuTGi_XflgE","image":{"url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-fRo860j0pTE/US5_M2S13xI/AAAAAAAAEFI/oP7QZqngKUk/w497-h373/retina.jpg","type":"image/jpeg","height":373,"width":497},"fullImage":{"url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-fRo860j0pTE/US5_M2S13xI/AAAAAAAAEFI/oP7QZqngKUk/retina.jpg","type":"image/jpeg","height":186,"width":271}}]},"provider":{"title":"Google+"},"access":{"kind":"plus#acl"}}